      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "With some testing I can confirm that any unspent recent tx (in my pruned database) are indeed visible, as mentioned in 3220. \r\nAny spent tx seems to be unreadable.\r\n\r\nNot sure about the rawmempool, but I assume it acts the same (spent unreadable, unspent readable).\r\n\r\nIdeally getrawtransaction would also show me spent transactions but either way this is good enough for my use case. \r\n\r\nBut I do not think it's intended behaviour though as the documents say txindex and getrawtransaction should be incompatible. (keep it though! ð )\r\n\r\n",
