      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "IMO `getrawtransaction`, in disabled txindex mode, should not brows the blocks your have store locally because that could consume a serious amount of resources (assume you have pruned to 100GB). For that, a call `searchrawtransaction` would be more appropriate.\r\n\r\nCurrent master (next 0.16 release) will allow to fetch a transaction with `getrawtransaction` from a specific block : #10275.",
